{"tid":1828033,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"[有圖] 32D鄧紫棋床上玩擘髀：叫我金毛獅紫！","createTime":"2020-01-17T12:34:00.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-18T12:04:08.000Z","uid":71632,"like":6,"dislike":61,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"21a371e373969e479746ecdd8b1f23b3e5c2b454","tid":1828033,"uid":71632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-17T12:34:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20200114/photo/bkn-20200114083734763-0114_00862_001_01p.jpg?20200114085836\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20200114%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20200114083734763-0114_00862_001_01p.jpg%3F20200114085836&h=e6790540&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n佢話呢身係金毛獅紫喎。<br />\n新一年唔少人都會以新形象示人，希望有個新開始！歌手鄧紫棋（G.E.M.）亦都唔例外，喺網上晒出一張新照，見佢一頭蓬鬆嘅頭髮，化身做「金毛獅紫」，再加埋佢着上一身粉紅色嘅套裝，坐喺床上大擺甫士兼騷美腿，呢個新造型睇到大家都嘩一聲，皆因從來未見過阿G.E.M.呢個look，而G.E.M.都話：「我好像很少穿粉紅色」唔知大家對佢呢個新look又點睇呢?"},{"pid":"04dc8247436d9e527609be829d4bcefee3fce501","tid":1828033,"uid":76098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-17T12:34:48.000Z","msg":"唔影埋腳趾?"},{"pid":"b8346fc917ed73afe453aa762a55d586f4ef8bb3","tid":1828033,"uid":71632,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"04dc8247436d9e527609be829d4bcefee3fce501","tid":1828033,"uid":76098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-17T12:34:48.000Z","msg":"唔影埋腳趾?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-17T12:41:37.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/p/B7QSLYZnBOI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FB7QSLYZnBOI%2F&d=qHKTGL1WilUkyN31MLoEKKGvShGfzVnrv2JJWMS0YvQ%3D&h=104df26f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FB7QSLYZnBOI%2F&h=abf170b3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/p/B7QSLYZnBOI/</a><br />\n入去問佢"},{"pid":"abae0a664b36ce3bd75d235c1d1a5b5c017b6096","tid":1828033,"uid":191815,"like":10,"dislike":4,"score":6,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-01-17T